{"tid":1648614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【法政巴絲】我係義務律師 你問我答","createTime":"2019-10-12T09:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T10:09:37.000Z","uid":272200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"98e2bd5490b9af8b97b656f60f72ee2692cde2ec","tid":1648614,"uid":272200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問：義務律師係咪真係義務㗎？<br />\n<br />\n答：雖然612基金其中一個目的就係為被捕人士籌措律師費，但小妹留意到幾個主要嘅義務律師團（包括小妹參與嗰個）為被捕人士被拘捕後48小時內（直到警察保釋或帶上法庭之前），所提供嘅任何法律支援，都不會向被捕人士收取任何費用 ，亦不會向612基金claim錢。佢 &middot; 哋 &middot; 真 &middot; 係 &middot; 義 &middot; 務 &middot; 㗎！</blockquote> <br />\n<blockquote>最後，小妹想講嘅係，義務律師有不少都係熱血嘅年輕律師，佢哋好多其實都未完全符合當值律師或法援署嘅要求（尤其係後者），未可以作為正式審訊時嘅代表律師。而資歷較深嘅義務律師，好多根本就冇打算要612基金幫手畀律師費。呢啲律師之所以參與義務律師嘅工作，就係純粹想幫被捕人士。可以成為佢哋嘅一分子，係小妹嘅光榮，衷心多謝你哋。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔知點講，香港人今次真係齊上齊落得好好，好感動！<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191012/60143120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F60143120&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=d1b6520d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F60143120&h=9ecba280\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191012/60143120</a>"},{"pid":"9224088b4382fd6a9a777247d782d94294d38652","tid":1648614,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:50:00.000Z","msg":"義務律師點維持生活?"},{"pid":"97f6ddd578e3b8baf870fc368037df488e8d092a","tid":1648614,"uid":56043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9224088b4382fd6a9a777247d782d94294d38652","tid":1648614,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:50:00.000Z","msg":"義務律師點維持生活?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"我相信一段時間義務無收入都無問題<br />\n只要本身有理財規劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}